{"tid":1653332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國參議員話要停止街頭暴力, 唔代表要停止勇武抗爭","createTime":"2019-10-14T04:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T10:13:59.000Z","uid":48667,"like":82,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"baae6f81aa601e49102dea157675ef74c63f651c","tid":1653332,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"首先都係個句, 希望大家唔好對個法案有太大期望<br />\n呢條法案通過左係有幫助,但絕對唔係靈丹妙藥,<br />\n佢既效果亦唔係一時三刻就會立即顯現<br />\n但呢條法案通過左既話, 就多一樣武器對抗港共以及中共政權<br />\n<br />\n跟住大家應該有睇到呢單新聞<br />\n郭榮鏗引述克魯茲籲停止暴力 參議院情況不穩 或有參議員反對 商界反對力度高 有人嘗試以香港街頭暴力畫面阻礙法案通過<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1653034\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1653034</a><br />\n<br />\n可能有部份人理解為&quot;應該要停止勇武抗爭&quot;, 甚至乎&quot;勇武退場, 勇武休息&quot;<br />\n但我對郭榮鏗所講既&quot;街頭暴力畫面&quot; 既理解, 係講緊裝修呢一類<br />\n而唔係面對黑警濫暴既時候所作出既反抗<br />\n<br />\n我認為勇武從來唔需要退場, 一直以黎都係講緊不分和勇,<br />\n到呢一刻都更加要堅守呢個信念,<br />\n所以我地係應該再將勇武抗爭既行動, 暫時轉移返去政府同黑警,<br />\n老實講, 經過咁多日既裝修, 我諗福建幫, 美心, 中資個堆都傷哂(銀行可能影響就細啲)<br />\n呢類既鋪頭應該交返俾裝飾手足同文宣手足應付<br />\n<del>至少等佢地換返哂啲新野先再裝修都未遲</del> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於人權法案個方面, 我認同有位巴打所講,<br />\n唔應該係我地單方面改變行動去令人權法通過,<br />\n所以其實國際既遊說工作都好重要,<br />\n之前有份去遊說既大專學界代表團, 都出左唔少力<br />\n之前搞左個眾籌都未夠錢,<br />\n希望有錢既人都可以出下錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKHIIAD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKHIIAD%2F&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=60f3e75e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKHIIAD/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚, 19:00 遮打花園見!!"},{"pid":"46d8bb6afedce668c6a8dd67c3e3464cb7675eed","tid":1653332,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:42:34.000Z","msg":"無人理"},{"pid":"133d0e3df8ef30b082a4959e477b41b1f29d9bb3","tid":1653332,"uid":217185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"5550dea3eb9a68f9357ae7d9537d55a712243d7f","tid":1653332,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:43:33.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n今晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa1e0bf9899fc2ced10ba90838fdac4f3fa3cd2","tid":1653332,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:45:04.000Z","msg":"反抗狗隻濫暴當然無問題la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8272031d772bde24d3f6c6e5b9b57955e53ca64f","tid":1653332,"uid":51752,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"勇武唔可以停<br />\n一停就endgame"},{"pid":"302c3fd01e28412423d1b954ccceae37e690e220","tid":1653332,"uid":67118,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8272031d772bde24d3f6c6e5b9b57955e53ca64f","tid":1653332,"uid":51752,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"勇武唔可以停<br />\n一停就endgame"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"無人叫勇武停 係要轉一轉方式<br />\n唔一定要直接衝突架嘛"},{"pid":"36e1609546f43725576ba05103058083bc365e37","tid":1653332,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:51:25.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9f23daa75eef35f993b3c382df621c565342a7a5","tid":1653332,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:52:24.000Z","msg":"push !!"},{"pid":"adf75f6053772450222c34bf4640f5fcc3b35f63","tid":1653332,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"覺得無錯既就推俾多啲人睇！！"},{"pid":"4953b547a0e73f3b3c9cb78c8bf05c78ae37db14","tid":1653332,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:53:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b717b20f7f6334fe5cbaac98858c86247d385c6f","tid":1653332,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"即係好似之前7.1個次咁？"},{"pid":"5d8553754e744a575eb967b9b17187e49da39f9c","tid":1653332,"uid":48667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"